# Netlify Redirects and Headers Configuration

# Redirect default Netlify subdomain to custom domain (optional - update with your domain)
# https://besorah-yeshua.netlify.app/* https://www.besorahyeshua.org/:splat 301!

# Single Page Application routing (if needed in future)
# /* /index.html 200

# Force HTTPS
# http://besorahyeshua.org/* https://besorahyeshua.org/:splat 301!

# Redirect common misspellings or old URLs
/home /index.html 301
/home.html /index.html 301

# 404 handling
# /404.html 404

## Security Headers
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()

## Cache Control Headers
/styles/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/scripts/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/*.html
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate